<div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Majorcan writer and philosopher (c. 1232 – 1316)</div>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1236090951">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}@media print{body.ns-0 .mw-parser-output .hatnote{display:none!important}}</style>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Ramon_Llull_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Ramon Llull (disambiguation)">Ramon Llull (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1236090951">
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Llull" redirects here. For the Spanish basketball player, see <a href="/wiki/Sergio_Llull" title="Sergio Llull">Sergio Llull</a>. For the medieval Spanish businesswoman, see <a href="/wiki/Caterina_Llull_i_Sabastida" title="Caterina Llull i Sabastida">Caterina Llull i Sabastida</a>.</div>
